summary: Memorandum regarding a meeting with AMBUNNY-1 and AMWHIP-1 to discuss a possible operation involving the penetration of UNSNAFU-19 office. Concerns are raised about AMBUNNY-1's background and the risk it poses to AMWHIP-1's connections. The possibility of using a cutout is suggested. A planned operation in Paris is canceled, but AMBUNNY-1 may be utilized in Rabat.
title: Meeting with AMBUNNY-1 and AMWHIP-1
